cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.HC, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with a computer vision problem of hand recognition using shape and texture-based features. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves feature extraction and matching, which are common tasks in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. The system proposed in the paper has potential applications in human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and biometrics (cs.LG).
